    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挥洒想象，打造属于你的终极飞艇！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《回音：飞艇建造器》是一款独立体验，你可以使用与完整版生存RPG《回音：飞艇传说》相同的核心系统，将最天马行空的飞艇创意变为现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/df4066595e9a1dcf21c475b50cc39977.poster.avif?t=1762878796\" width=615 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/df4066595e9a1dcf21c475b50cc39977.webm?t=1762878796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >船体、风帆、防御系统、内部结构……每一个细节都由你说了算。威武的空中堡垒、敏捷的侦察舰、奢华的浮空宫殿……天空任你驰骋，带来无限可能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/e2de44756a43a8df7e47bf266c96050b.poster.avif?t=1762878796\" width=615 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/e2de44756a43a8df7e47bf266c96050b.webm?t=1762878796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的作品不仅是静态飞艇，更是未来的起点！一旦《回音：飞艇传说》正式上线，你的飞艇将作为游戏内飞艇蓝图，助你抢占先机、遨游高空，充分迎接挑战。快来建造飞艇，未来蓄势待发！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/9873a32a31aba794fe6476aaf89afc02.webp?t=1762878796\" width=615 height=36 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入社区，为荣耀而战！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/948b091111c622afd73b5f93d772880a.poster.avif?t=1762878796\" width=615 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/948b091111c622afd73b5f93d772880a.webm?t=1762878796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们期待见证你的飞艇腾空而起！请在社交媒体上使用关键词标签 #AirshipBuilder 分享你的作品，就有机会登上我们的社区精选。关注我们的社交平台，获取更多精彩更新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一望无际的天空在呼唤着，你准备好打造属于你的传奇了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269310/extras/9873a32a31aba794fe6476aaf89afc02.webp?t=1762878796\" width=615 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>  </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>完整游戏内容抢先看</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《回音：飞艇传说》中，你将驾驶专属飞艇翱翔天际，探索浮空岛屿，揭开远古秘密，并与钟械军团展开激战。无论是独自冒险还是与好友并肩作战，你的飞艇都将是你的终极基地，伴你在这个充满危险、谜团与冒险的世界中勇往直前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>现在就将 《回音：飞艇传说》 加入愿望单吧！随时掌握完整版游戏的最新动态，抢先一窥游戏开发进展！</p>",
